f","tid":662103,"uid":77473,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T07:06:17.000Z","msg":"水 因為要夠疊水先買到"},{"pid":"adccb22cf8bab1e1632b7e6cb45ee62228204451","tid":662103,"uid":9566,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T07:07:52.000Z","msg":"全能系 因為集齊五系佢先咁硬"},{"pid":"7d9ea2f94437a93e9b9e8371826433617f9fc46d","tid":662103,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T08:29:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3e79d48b8e42e72ee0a32fba8ea44367561b582","tid":662103,"uid":3698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T08:49:09.000Z","msg":"睇部首"},{"pid":"b2cdb1e7393a1a6d288ceb7d518692e9a69f7cdc","tid":662103,"uid":5963,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T08:55:56.000Z","msg":"鑽石五行屬戊土"},{"pid":"31b84599fbecb774b54e48716784a54d03fb1797","tid":662103,"uid":44854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adccb22cf8bab1e1632b7e6cb45ee62228204451","tid":662103,"uid":9566,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T07:07:52.000Z","msg":"全能系 因為集齊五系佢先咁硬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T08:56:51.000Z","msg":"怕火"},{"pid":"41cbf632c8a7de23812042c4cead11c6077f65e5","tid":662103,"uid":5963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3e79d48b8e42e72ee0a32fba8ea44367561b582","tid":662103,"uid":3698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T08:49:09.000Z","msg":"睇部首"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:03:26.000Z","msg":"第二個字呢？"},{"pid":"011a24b20d05d8dbce429b1ec1c70bc69b5cadf9","tid":662103,"uid":77052,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b2cdb1e7393a1a6d288ceb7d518692e9a69f7cdc","tid":662103,"uid":5963,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T08:55:56.000Z","msg":"鑽石五行屬戊土"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:04:45.000Z","msg":"終於有個識嘢嘅人講<br />\n鑽石本身係碳元素嚟，碳本身五行屬土都係戊土嚟<br />\n所以鑽石自然都係戊土"},{"pid":"1fdccbc6d00dc4fb7355ab04ecb8bb576e7f392e","tid":662103,"uid":5963,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"76065ebb101e50eb3176025334e6f4b49f7f35e2","tid":662103,"uid":116774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:52:59.000Z","msg":"可唔可以解釋下"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:46:11.000Z","msg":"五行天干分陰陽，金分陽金「庚」，陰金「辛」，兩種係唔同既金屬<br />\n<br />\n庚金係硬金，帶煞既金，所以通常會引用為兵器，硬既金屬，鐵，鋼（後解）<br />\n<br />\n而辛金係軟金，（辛金溫軟清潤，非珠玉也），點解會話係非珠玉呢，因為辛金一直都比喻為貴金，首飾，所以有人會誤會玉石屬金，但係其實玉石係屬土，因為辛金要軟，所以辛金係貴金，金，銀類。<br />\n<br />\n而庚辛係唔可以互換，金銀不能成兵，就算成兵都係用黎收藏非煞器，鐵鋼能成器，但不貴，就算成器都唔會有人珍惜，唔辛苦咁拎到。<br />\n<br />\n而點解個人覺得鑽石唔係屬金而係屬土呢，就要睇五行關係，火克金，金一直都怕火，硬金屬要用火煉先會成器，煉鐵煉鋼，而軟金就更怕火，一燒就會熔，所以金遇火會轉變型態，而鑽石極硬，成型唔需要用火，又唔怕火，話佢係硬金又唔帶煞，覺得佢貴重而話佢係軟金又唔怕火。<br />\n<br />\n而睇下土同火既關係，火生土，火燒完既灰燼會成土，鑽石由咩組成？炭，而仲有一樣就係鑽石成器既經過，係琢而成器，玉不琢不成器，所以鑽石同玉石一樣但同金唔同。所以我覺得鑽石屬土"},{"pid":"645a7678ecce12995413e3b4c47399a7385887a9","tid":662103,"uid":5963,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:49:42.000Z","msg":"如果係因為戴乜鳩首飾，乜鳩玉石屬乜就真係算撚數，水晶玉石唔理咩顏色都係屬土，金銀貴錶屬金，講撚完"},{"pid":"e62b3e91cc73a405f160d41ee21d01279109b75d","tid":662103,"uid":5963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:50:54.000Z","msg":"戊土屬陽土，硬土，多為山石"},{"pid":"5e78425efa529a43526729a1205e7b1d1ca3bd73","tid":662103,"uid":5963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60f4901f0ee8c96bd770017fb3da9a3dd53da67f","tid":662103,"uid":77473,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T07:06:17.000Z","msg":"水 因為要夠疊水先買到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:55:54.000Z","msg":"哈哈，土克水，八字水為財，買撚完就少忽身家"},{"pid":"2eae350bdfe0acc059ee627f5e37128c6d509ef6","tid":662103,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:58:11.000Z","msg":"Earth/地"},{"pid":"451b6d088032e7c46eafb9cd450407c7113e2690","tid":662103,"uid":83784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T10:06:01.000Z","msg":"鑽石係屬於我既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25ea5b13b6ed5f5f3e16363a893aadfad79b9e4","tid":662103,"uid":116774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T12:06:01.000Z","msg":"題外話 咁本身個人屬水，咁鑽石屬土，咁土剋水，咪唔岩？"},{"pid":"2dc4cc52c73da2123a9fd07e473253897a0ae6b5","tid":662103,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T13:09:17.000Z","msg":"五行論除左storytelling之外, 今時今日仲有咩實際價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}